## Dispatch Rules

For each format in the `formats` list, delegate to the appropriate sub-template:

| Format | Template | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `pdf` | `kindle-zip/export-pdf` | Generate PDF with title page, embedded TOC, flowing text |
| `epub` | `kindle-zip/export-epub-page` | Generate EPUB 3.0 ZIP with XHTML chapters |
| `markdown` | `kindle-zip/export-markdown` | Generate Markdown with heading hierarchy |
| `txt` | (inline) | Plain text — no formatting needed |

For each generated file:
1. Write to `{{ output_dir }}/{{ asin }}/book.{ext}`
2. Record the file path, format, and byte size.
3. Emit a CNS span `kindle-zip.export.{format}` with size and duration.

After all formats are generated, emit an aggregate CNS span with total bytes and format list.

